     FUNCTION IN 4.0                 HOTKEY IN 4.0                FUNCTION IN 4.0                HOTKEY IN 4.0


                                                     Transform
        Move (Grab)                         G                Transform with locked Axis          G/R/S + MMB
   Move along global axis              G + X/Y/Z                      Duplicate                     Shift + D
    Move along local axis            G + XX/YY/ZZ                 Duplicate Linked                   Alt + D
            Scale                           S                     Apply Transform                    Ctrl + A
   Scale along global axis              S + X/Y/Z                  Reset Position                    Alt + G
    Scale along local axis           S + XX/YY/ZZ                  Reset Rotation                    Alt + R
           Rotate                           R                        Reset Scale                     Alt + S
  Rotate along global axis             R + X/Y/Z                  Snapping Toggle                  Shift + Tab
   Rotate along local axis           R + XX/YY/ZZ                  Set Snap Base                        B
        Free Rotate                       R+R


                                                      Selection
           Select                         LMB¹                     Select Grouped                   Shift + G
          Select All                        A                      Invert Selection                  Ctrl + I
        Deselect All             Alt + A (doubletap A)              Select Linked                   Shift + L
       Border Select                B or Drag LMB              Pick from Overlapping               Alt + LMB
        Circle Select                       C


                                                       Modes
     Edit/Object Mode                     Tab                   All Modes (Pie Menu)               Ctrl + Tab


                                                       Menus
      Tool Shelf Toggle                     T                      Quick Favorites                      Q
       Sidebar Toggle                       N                        Add Menu³                      Shift + A
   Object Context Menu                   RMB²                      Pivot Pie Menu                       .
   Orientation Pie Menu                     ,                    Snapping Pie Menu                  Shift + S


¹ You can choose either Left Click (default) or Right Click Select in the Preferences under Input.
² If you have chosen Right Click Select (in the Preferences under Input), the Object Context Menu is accessible via the
W key.
³ Now also works in the Modifier Tab.




