                                                 SCULPTING
     FUNCTION IN 4.0                 HOTKEY IN 4.0                FUNCTION IN 4.0             HOTKEY IN 4.0


                                                        Control
         Brush Size                         F                    Switch Sculpt Object        Hover + Alt + Q
       Brush Strength                   Shift + F             Set Transform Pivot Gizmo        Shift + RMB
        Brush Angle                      Ctrl + F


                                                        Masking
            Mask                            M                 Expand Mask by Curvature       Shift + Alt + A*
         Clear Mask                      Alt + M                      Invert Mask                Ctrl + I
 Expand Mask by Topology                Shift + A                      Box Mask                     B


                                                        Brushes
            Draw                            V                            Pose             Shift + Space, Shift 1*
            Grab                            G                           Nudge             Shift + Space, Shift 2*
           Inflate                           I                       Rotate Brush         Shift + Space, Shift 3*
        Snake Hook                          K                         Slide Relax         Shift + Space, Shift 4*
            Pinch                           P                          Boundary           Shift + Space, Shift 5*
           Smooth                   S or Shift + Drag                    Cloth            Shift + Space, Shift 6*
         Clay Strips                        C                           Simplify          Shift + Space, Shift 7*
           Crease                       Shift + C               Multires Displ. Eraser    Shift + Space, Shift 0*
           Scrape                       Shift + T               Multires Displ. Smear     Shift + Space, Ctrl 1*
        Draw Sharp                  Shift + Space, 1*                  Box Hide           Shift + Space, Ctrl 6*
             Clay                   Shift + Space, 2*                  Box Trim           Shift + Space, Ctrl 9*
        Clay Thumb                  Shift + Space, 3*                Line Project         Shift + Space, Alt 1*
            Layer                   Shift + Space, 4*                 Mesh Filter         Shift + Space, Alt 2*
            Blob                    Shift + Space, 5*                 Cloth Filter        Shift + Space, Alt 3*
           Flatten                  Shift + Space, 6*                    Move             Shift + Space, Alt 5*
             Fill                   Shift + Space, 7*                 Transform           Shift + Space, Alt 6*
     Mutiplane Scrape               Shift + Space, 8*                   Rotate            Shift + Space, Alt 7*
       Elastic Deform               Shift + Space, 9*                    Scale            Shift + Space, Alt 8*
           Thumb                    Shift + Space, 0*


* only accessible if the spacebar function is set to Play in the Preferences.




