                                                      Face Sets
       Draw Face Sets            Shift + Space, Shift 9*             Edit Face Set        Shift + Space, Ctrl W*
        Box Face Set             Shift + Space, Ctrl 7*           Show all Face Sets             Alt + H
    Face Sets Pie Menu                   Alt + W                 Hide Active Face Set               H
   Grow/Shrink Face Set         Ctrl + W / Ctrl + Alt + W       Hide Inactive Face Sets         Shift + H


                                                       Painting
            Paint                Shift + Space, Ctrl 2*               Color Filter        Shift + Space, Alt 4*
           Smear                 Shift + Space, Ctrl 3*             Mask by Color         Shift + Space, Alt 5*


