                                   Shader Editor, Geo Nodes, Compositing
           Group                         Ctrl + G               Delete with Reconnect           Ctrl + X
          Ungroup                     Ctrl + Alt + G                Insert Reroute         Shift + RMB + Drag
     Edit Group Toggle                     Tab                  Hide Unused Sockets             Ctrl + H
     Join in New Frame                   Ctrl + J                   Minimize Node                  H
          Cut Links                Ctrl + RMB + Drag                  Mute Node                    M
         Mute Links             Ctrl + Alt + RMB + Drag      Skip Auto Node Attachment             Alt


                                                     Compositing
  Background Image Move                Alt + MMB             Background Image Zoom in            Alt + V
Background Image Zoom out                   V


                                                     Image Editor
         New Image                       Alt + N                      Save Image                 Alt + S
        Open Image                       Alt + O                    Save Image As            Shift + Alt + S


                                                       UV Editor
         Mark Seam                       Ctrl + E                        Stitch                  Alt + V
         Select Split                       Y                             Pin                      P
   Grow/Shrink Selection                Ctrl + +/-                      Unpin                    Alt + P


                                                        Painting
        Sample Color                     Shift X                   Brush Colors Flip               X
         Brush Size                         F                 Select Faces for Face Mask       Alt + LMB
       Brush Strength                   Shift + F            Expand Face Mask Selection     Alt + Shift + LMB
       Stroke Method                      Alt + E


                                                    Texture Painting
            Draw                    Shift + Space, 1*                    Clone              Shift + Space, 4*
           Soften                   Shift + Space, 2*                     Fill              Shift + Space, 5*
           Smear                    Shift + Space, 3*                    Mask               Shift + Space, 6*


* only accessible if the spacebar function is set to Play in the Preferences.




